name: Online Media Masters
tag_list: internet-marketing, seo, search-engine-optimization, social-media, sem, google-analytics, linkedin-profiles
overview:
Online Media Masters provides internet marketing services for small and medium-sized businesses in Chicago, IL.

We build and markets websites and brands online. We use WordPress for all website design and on-page search engine optimization. Outside of a website, we do link building, social media marketing, local marketing through online directory submission, and even Google Analytics.

Our team has ranked the #1 “artist” worldwide in LinkedIn, follow all recommendations made in Google’s official SEO guide, and have create beautiful website for individuals and companies in a variety of industries.
